1
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,080
Hello, Sheriff.

2
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,770
Father-in-law.

3
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:44,759
They say

4
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,520
you will be executed in two days.

5
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,600
Sometimes I really

6
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,620
feel sorry for you.

7
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,400
And for Wangshu too.

8
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,880
It's all Chen Jiadong's fault.

9
00:01:58,320 --> 00:01:59,450
Sometimes I wonder,

10
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,440
if back then,

11
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,800
if you had

12
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:02,560
chosen me earlier

13
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,360
to be your son-in-law, would you

14
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:06,460
have avoided ending up like this?

15
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:08,919
Choose you?

16
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,120
Unless I die,

17
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,800
my daughter would

18
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,480
never marry someone like you.

19
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,840
You despicable villain.

20
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:23,960
Old Lin.

21
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,690
I might as well tell you.

22
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,600
Yamada and I

23
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,200
have already surrounded the execution ground.

24
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:37,200
I'm just waiting for your daughter,

25
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,680
your son,

26
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,320
and Chen Jiadong

27
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,610
to come back and fall into the trap.

28
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,840
At worst, I'll send all four

29
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
of your family on your way together.

30
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,000
Then you won't be lonely.

31
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,690
Stop your wishful thinking, Luo Wang.

32
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,040
Before they left,

33
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,240
I told them

34
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,800
no matter what happens,

35
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,680
they shouldn't come back.

36
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,160
They won't come back.

37
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,400
You're wrong.

38
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,820
They will come back

39
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,940
because they want to save you.

40
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,530
When they come back to save you,

41
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:20,600
I will watch

42
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,920
them die one

43
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,760
by one in front of you.

44
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:31,760
I will make you watch them die.

45
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,940
Keep a close eye on him.

46
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,400
If anything happens,

47
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,220
report to me immediately.

48
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,000
Yes.

49
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,080
I'm going to deliver food to Mr. Li.

50
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,720
Every day, I come in through this door,

51
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,240
and then,

52
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,840
after delivering all the meals,

53
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,480
I go out.

54
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:12,840
Zheng.

55
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,760
Every time you go in and out,

56
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,420
do they inspect you strictly?

57
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,680
I deliver every day, so we're familiar.

58
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,200
A simple greeting is enough.

59
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,920
The crucial step

60
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,160
hasn't been figured out yet.

61
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,040
You mean

62
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,160
Yamada?

63
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,280
Yeah.

64
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,320
Catching Yamada is the key.

65
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,000
Are you sure you can do it?

66
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,600
Yamada is watching the square.

67
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,930
How will you make a move?

68
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,480
If we don't catch Yamada,

69
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,330
all our efforts will be wasted.

70
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:37,840
Mr. Qin,

71
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,240
I have investigated.

72
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,560
Yamada is

73
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,610
a womanizer.

74
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,840
He goes to Hua Street at dusk

75
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,720
to have fun.

76
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,770
Then we'll catch him at Hua Street.

77
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,520
Hua Street is

78
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,760
a very chaotic place.

79
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,200
If we make even a little noise,

80
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,530
we'll be in big trouble.

81
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,080
There is Fen Alley next to the flower street.

82
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,440
It's quiet with few people.

83
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,900
We can make our move there.

84
00:04:59,159 --> 00:04:59,840
Okay.

85
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,800
Then tonight at 9:00 PM,

86
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,930
we stick to the plan.

87
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,600
Sir, you're here again.

88
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,940
I'm here, I'm here.

89
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,360
Sir,

90
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,800
do you want to come home with me

91
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,480
so I can sing Nanyin for you?

92
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,680
Very well.

93
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,960
I want you.

94
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,240
Come with me.

95
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,920
Where are you taking me?

96
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,600
Me?

97
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:04,960
I'm taking you to my house.

98
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,520
Wangshu.

99
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,320
Silly girl.

100
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,340
It's too risky.

101
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,400
Jiadong,

102
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,720
calm down.

103
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,040
Sir, just follow me.

104
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,560
Sir, be careful.

105
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,120
Be careful.

106
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,880
Beautiful,

107
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:26,240
where do you live?

108
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,440
I

109
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,920
live just up ahead.

110
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,960
It's just at the end of the alley.

111
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,240
Sir.

112
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,159
Come here.

113
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,520
You are being ridiculous.

114
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,320
Chen Jiadong.

115
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,640
We just got married and you're already yelling at me.

116
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,720
How could you come to a place like this?

117
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,720
It's too dangerous.

118
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,360
No matter how dangerous it is,

119
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,360
I have to save my father.

120
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:56,820
Well...

121
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,860
You should have told me first.

122
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,370
Would you have let me come if I told you?

123
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,560
All right, all right.

124
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,360
Stop wasting time.

125
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,000
Saving him is more important. Let's go.

126
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,060
Brother, let's go.

127
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,090
Zheng Yi.

128
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,360
Who is this?

129
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:18,120
My cousin.

130
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,360
My rheumatism is acting up, and my legs hurt.

131
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,120
So I asked him to help me push the cart.

132
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:23,680
By the way.

133
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,410
I've already told Captain Luo.

134
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,460
Please take care of us.

135
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,120
As long as you've told him.

136
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,760
Go on in.

137
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,360
Brothers,

138
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,780
I brought some food especially for you guys.

139
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,720
And some wine.

140
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,840
Come on.

141
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,080
You're a sensible kid.

142
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,540
You know how to think of us.

143
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,280
Exactly.

144
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,120
That's right.

145
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,840
Let me have a drink with you, brothers.

146
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,320
You go deliver the food first.

147
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:58,960
Go ahead.

148
00:07:59,520 --> 00:07:59,960
Go.

149
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,360
Mr. Zheng is the best.

150
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,780
He always thinks of us.

151
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,840
Come.

152
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,240
Dad.

153
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:25,560
Dad.

154
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:28,490
Mingshu.

155
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,320
Dad.

156
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,760
Dad. Mingshu.

157
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:34,730
Why are you here?

158
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,679
Dad.

159
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,500
I'm here to get you out.

160
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,320
No.

161
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,400
It's too dangerous.

162
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,039
Go now.

163
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:41,760
Dad.

164
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:42,919
We have a plan.

165
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,290
Let's get out first.

166
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,770
Dad, hold on here first.

167
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,720
Hold tight.

168
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,320
The medicine works well.

169
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,440
What are you doing?

170
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,040
Your son-in-law's plan.

171
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,040
A bait and switch.

172
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,200
What?

173
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,500
No time to explain.

174
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,440
You have to hide in here.

175
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,640
I'll take you out first.

176
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,160
Okay.

177
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,280
Dad, be careful.

178
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,320
I lost.

179
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,200
Come, come.

180
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,400
Place your bets.

181
00:09:58,680 --> 00:09:59,640
Big.

182
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,360
Come on.

183
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,200
Place your bets.

184
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,280
Big or small?

185
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:06,810
Brother.

186
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,380
The food is delivered.

187
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,480
Quick, huh?

188
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,800
What do you think?

189
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,560
Guys,

190
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,240
I'll take off now.

191
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,400
I'll come back another day.

192
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,120
Okay.

193
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:19,800
Alright.

194
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:21,220
Let's drink later.

195
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,330
I'm leaving.

196
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,640
Wait.
